ps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-vouchers-school-choice-block-grants-public-funding-private-education-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20school%20voucher%20movement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Some%20districts%20have%20had%20to%20shut%20down%20schools%20as%20a%20result%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feducation-department-funding-staff-cuts-students-schools-student-loans-trump-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Euncertainty%20with%20federal%20funding%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20added%20strain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20teachers%20and%20administrators%20in%20Broward%20County%2C%20Florida%20%E2%80%94%20a%20county%20that%20has%20faced%20steep%20enrollment%20declines%20%E2%80%94%20to%20learn%20how%20schools%20are%20fighting%20to%20keep%20their%20doors%20open.%20The%20efforts%20include%20parent%20tours%2C%20showcases%2C%20innovative%20marketing%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20the%20one%20doing%20every%20school%20tour%2C%20all%2060%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Stephanie%20Saban%2C%20the%20principal%20at%20Coral%20Cove%20Academy%20of%20the%20Arts%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20held%20two%20showcases%20in%20the%20neighborhood%2C%20and%20we%20invited%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20community%20out%20to%20see%20our%20performances.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Students%20at%20Coral%20Cove%20Academy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6900db3a0be9845f2dc53ab9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222857%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESchool%20administrators%20in%20Broward%20County%20frequently%20showcase%20their%20programs%20to%20attract%20and%20retain%20families.%3Cp%3EAlfonso%20Duran%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20private%20schools%20and%20charter%20schools%20can%20call%20parents%20and%20market%20what%20they%20offer%2C%20public%20schools%20should%20be%20doing%20the%20same%2C%20Stephens%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20believe%20in%20school%20choice%20but%20you%20don't%20want%20public%20schools%20to%20compete%2C%20then%20you%20don't%20really%20believe%20in%20school%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20Stephens%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269601ccb-16b8-48b7-8967-77b2bb2f5b1f%5C%22%3E'Constant%20showcasing%20the%20program'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGastride%20Harrigan%2C%20the%20principal%20at%20Millennium%206-12%20Collegiate%20Academy%20in%20Broward%20County%2C%20knows%20that%20marketing%20is%20a%20crucial%20element%20of%20his%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20a%20big%20%26quot%3Bselling%20point%26quot%3B%20for%20parents%20is%20that%20the%20school%20offers%20students%20the%20opportunity%20to%20graduate%20with%20both%20an%20associate%20degree%20and%20a%20high%20school%20diploma%2C%20and%20he%20makes%20sure%20to%20promote%20that%20whenever%20he%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompetition%20is%20fierce%2C%20and%20it's%20constant%20showcasing%20the%20program%2C%26quot%3B%20Harrigan%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20focuses%20on%20building%20relationships%20with%20the%20feeder%20elementary%20school%2C%20which%20means%20going%20to%20their%20meetings%20and%20events%20and%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20sure%20parents%20understand%20who%20we%20are%2C%20what%20we%20offer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20it's%20not%20just%20speaking%20about%20the%20programs%20Millennium%20offers%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20including%20students%20in%20the%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20hear%20from%20the%20kids%20who%20go%20through%20the%20program%2C%20whether%20in%20middle%20or%20high%2C%20then%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20better%20selling%20point%20than%20me%20trying%20to%20tell%20you%20the%20benefits%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Harrigan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20December%209%2C%20Broward%20County%20Public%20Schools%20is%20holding%20a%20showcase%20to%20advertise%20opportunities%20at%20schools%20county-wide.%20The%20flyer%20for%20the%20showcase%20said%20that%20families%20will%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20county's%20K-12%20magnet%20programs%2C%20%26quot%3Binnovative%26quot%3B%20curriculum%20offerings%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bunique%20programs%20tailored%20to%20student%20success.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENortheast%20High%20School's%20principal%2C%20Anthony%20Valachovic%2C%20embraces%20this%20strategy.%20His%20school%20promotes%20its%20ACEs%20program%2C%20which%20allows%20students%20to%20pursue%20an%20educational%20pathway%20tailored%20to%20aviation%2C%20technology%2C%20or%20the%20arts.%20The%20school's%20magnet%20coordinator%20goes%20to%20showcases%2C%20local%20sports%20games%2C%20and%20other%20community%20events%20to%20get%20the%20word%20out.%20It's%20working%3A%20on%20the%2010th%20day%20of%20the%20current%20academic%20year%2C%20Northeast%20enrolled%201%2C822%20students%2C%20compared%20to%201%2C689%20at%20the%20same%20time%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20boils%20down%20to%20finding%20programs%20that%20match%20the%20students'%20interests%20and%20really%20tailoring%20what%20you're%20doing%20to%20your%20actual%20school%20population%2C%26quot%3B%20Valochovic%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchools%20can't%20control%20some%20of%20the%20factors%20contributing%20to%20tanking%20enrollment%2C%20like%20declining%20birth%20rates.%20But%20they%20can%20control%20their%20messaging%2C%20and%20Stephens%20said%20now%20is%20a%20critical%20time%20for%20them%20to%20shape%20their%20own%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPublic%20schools%20are%20getting%20more%20and%20more%20in%20the%20game%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Stephens%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20a%20good%20sign%2C%20and%20could%20be%20awesome%20for%20us%20as%20a%20nation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpublic-school-marketing-declining-enrollment-public-charter-competition-2025-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3