20business%20saw%20a%2055%25%20increase%20this%20year%20compared%20to%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EF45's%20Wilson%20said%20he's%20also%20seen%20an%20increase%20in%20corporate%20interest%20since%20the%20pandemic%2C%20especially%20from%20entertainment%20and%20media%20companies%2C%20since%20he's%20based%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20teaching%20classes%20in%20offices%20and%20studios%2C%20he%20travels%20to%20lead%20workouts%20at%20conferences%20and%20corporate%20gatherings%2C%20ranging%20from%2030-minute%20team-building%20sweat%20sessions%20to%20full%20wellness%20programming%20built%20into%20multi-day%20conferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilson%20said%20F45%20has%20gone%20from%20booking%20an%20average%20of%20one%20corporate%20fitness%20event%20a%20month%20at%20an%20off-site%20or%20conference%2C%20to%20as%20many%20as%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarry's%20executive%20VP%20of%20brand%20and%20communications%2C%20Vicky%20Land%20said%20that%20HR%20departments%20started%20to%20recognize%20that%20not%20everyone%20wanted%20to%20go%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-workout-networking-fitness-classes-with-clients-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edinner%20and%20drinks%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20coworkers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20much%20less%20likely%20to%20actually%20cancel%20a%20workout%20than%20they%20will%20be%20to%20text%20you%20that%20they're%20not%20going%20to%20come%20to%20drinks%2C%26quot%3B%20Land%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20employees%20see%20a%20personal%20benefit%20to%20attending%20a%20workout%20class%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20a%20networking%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20amid%20employers'%20push%20for%20RTO%2C%20Land%20said%20%26quot%3Bpop-up%20workouts%26quot%3B%20at%20offices%20have%20become%20yet%20another%20way%20to%20encourage%20workers%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-jpmorgan-office-tower-270-park-avenue-gym-membership-amenities-2025-8%5C%22%20targ