ual%20leaders%20to%20hear%20their%20ideas%20and%20concerns.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20polls%20are%20correct%2C%20Salem%20says%20CEOs%20they've%20invited%20have%20%26quot%3Bindicated%20that%20they're%20ready%20to%20join%20immediately%20after%20the%20election.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c9a12fcb-9911-4145-99e5-5fdfae7aa34c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20McKinsey%20to%20Mamdani%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESalem%2C%20a%20son%20of%20Egyptian%20immigrants%20who%20was%20raised%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20said%20the%20idea%20for%20the%20PAC%20came%20the%20night%20of%20Mamdani's%20primary%20landslide%2C%20while%20he%20was%20celebrating%20at%20the%20campaign's%20official%20watch%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20thought%20that%20if%20an%20NYU%20Stern%20and%20Harvard%20Business%20School%20graduate%20could%20join%20a%20bunch%20of%20progressive%20activists%2C%20maybe%20he%20could%20find%20some%20common%20ground%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzohran-mamdani-business-leaders-meeting-kathryn-wylde-partnership-nyc-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20York's%20business%20leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20Mamdani%20mayoralty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20unlikely%20revelation%20for%20someone%20whose%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20is%20packed%20with%20corporate%20strategy%20experience%2C%20not%20political%20organization.%20After%20a%20few%20banking%20internships%2C%20Salem's%20career%20took%20off%20with%20consulting%20powerhouse%20McKinsey%2C%20where%20he%20said%20he%20helped%20build%20infrastructure%20for%20the%20Saudi%20kingdom's%20response%20to%20the%20MERS%20virus%20in%202014.%20He%20also%20spent%20a%20year%20with%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20nearly%20%241%20trillion%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaudi-arabia-public-investment-fund-global-investment-spree-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPublic%20Investment%20Fund%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20sovereign%20wealth%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mamdani%20announced%20his%20run%20in%20late%202024%2C%20Salem%20was%20running%20Hira%20Ventures%2C%20his%20own%20small%20private%20advisory%20and%20investment%20firm%2C%20which%20built%20a%20Brooklyn-based%20urgent%20care%20clinic%20and%20a%20COVID-testing%20business%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20grew%20his%20businesses%2C%20he%20also%20expanded%20his%20network%20of%20New%20York's%20business%20and%20political%20power%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Salem%20first%20got%20a%20call%20late%20last%20year%20to%20meet%20Mamdani%20through%20a%20politically%20connected%20friend%2C%20he%20turned%20it%20down%2C%20he%20said.%20He%20was%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20deal%2C%20very%20busy.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20saw%20Mamdani%20polling%20at%201%25%20and%20thought%20Mamdani%20%26quot%3Beither%20doesn't%20know%20what%20he's%20saying%20isn't%20achievable%2C%20which%20is%20a%20problem%2C%20or%20he%20knows%20what%20he's%20saying%20isn't%20achievable%2C%20and%20that's%20even%20a%20bigger%20problem.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Mamdani's%20poll%20numbers%20and%20Instagram%20followers%20continued%20to%20rise%2C%20Salem%20decided%20he%20was%20judging%20the%20campaign%20like%20a%20consultant%20%E2%80%94%20expecting%20a%20five-year%20plan%20with%20milestones%20and%20metrics.%20But%20Mamdani%20wasn't%20offering%20a%20step-by-step%20blueprint%3B%20he%20was%20setting%20a%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20laying%20out%20big%20goals%2C%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Ban%20affordable%20New%20York%20for%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Salem%20said%2C%20Mamdani%20could%20be%20creating%20the%20energy%20and%20momentum%20to%20make%20change%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22377edeb7-b10b-44e6-af32-8b1103e93839%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESelling%20CEOs%20on%20a%20socialist's%20vision%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Salem%20set%20up%20OneNYC%2C%20he%20saw%20a%20way%20to%20get%20business%20leaders%20to%20%26quot%3Bdisregard%20distracting%20noise%2C%26quot%3B%20and