11-d3ec-4a68-b6d4-e56f3ac14703%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EInside%20Salem's%20conversations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMamdani's%20loudest%20critics%20have%20threatened%20that%20if%20he%20wins%2C%20the%20city's%20tax%20base%20will%20flee.%20A%20poll%20from%20Victory%20Insights%2C%20a%20right-leaning%20polling%20firm%2C%20reported%20that%20more%20than%20a%20quarter%20of%20New%20York%20City%20residents%20would%20consider%20leaving%20if%20Mamdani%20won.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalem%20doesn't%20think%20that%20will%20be%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarly%20on%2C%20I%20heard%20almost%20zero%20about%20taxes%2C%20which%20I%20found%20fascinating%2C%26quot%3B%20Salem%20said%20about%20his%20conversations%20with%20CEOs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchlosstein%20said%20that%20many%20of%20his%20peers%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20pay%20more%20if%20they%20felt%20the%20difference%20in%20quality%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20good%20number%20of%20those%20who%20are%20higher%20income%20are%20prepared%20to%20pay%20somewhat%20higher%20taxes%20in%20order%20to%20have%20a%20more%20successful%20city%2C%26quot%3B%20Schlosstein%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalem%20said%20that%20CEOs%20have%20highlighted%20three%20major%20concerns%3A%20Mamdani's%20lack%20of%20experience%2C%20public%20safety%20plans%2C%20and%20fears%20that%20his%20housing%20affordability%20program%20would%20backfire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESalem%20explained%20that%20a%20potential%20Tisch%20appointment%20showcases%20that%20Mamdani%20will%20put%20%26quot%3Bcapability%26quot%3B%20over%20%26quot%3Bideology%2C%26quot%3B%20helping%20allay%20concerns%20around%20his%20lack%20of%20experience%20or%20his%20plans%20for%20public%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20proposals%2C%20like%20free%20childcare%2C%20were%20easy%20for%20business%20leaders%20to%20understand.%20Others%2C%20like%20free%20buses%2C%20have%20required%20his%20background%20in%20advising%20to%20help%20people%20grasp%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuses%20were%20selected%20because%20eliminat