ns%20manager%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-meet-hangouts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Meet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20were%20magical%20in%20a%20way%20I%20could%20have%20never%20imagined.%20The%20job%20was%20challenging%2C%20and%20I%20got%20to%20collaborate%20with%20some%20of%20the%20best%20people%20I've%20ever%20encountered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20perfect%20on%20paper%2C%20but%20something%20was%20missing.%20As%20time%20went%20on%2C%20being%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20suffering%20I%20knew%20was%20happening%20in%20the%20world%20while%20growing%20money%20felt%20jarring.%20It%20was%20like%20being%20in%20Disneyland%20every%20day%3A%20the%20massage%20rooms%2C%20unlimited%20food%2C%20and%20other%20perks.%20But%20at%20some%20point%2C%20you%20get%20sick%20of%20Disneyland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20been%20keen%20on%20mission-driven%20work.%20Growing%20up%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20therapist%2C%20a%20teacher%2C%20or%20work%20at%20a%20nonprofit.%20After%20college%2C%20my%20goal%20was%20to%20pay%20off%20my%20student%20loans%20and%20build%20a%20safety%20net%20for%20my%20parents.%20I%20started%20my%20career%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faccenture-consulting-cut-staff-reskill-hiring-ai-era-sweet-earnings-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsulting%20at%20Accenture%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20working%20on%20tech%20strategy%2C%20which%20was%20challenging%20and%20interesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20in%20the%20workforce%20for%20a%20bit%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feffective-altruism-how-started-how-its-going-after-ftx-collapse-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeffective%20altruism%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20into%20the%20picture%20because%20of%20how%20comfortable%20I%20knew%20my%20life%20was%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20so%20many%20others%20lacked%20resources.%20I%20wished%20I%20could%20take%20less%20of%20what%20I%20had%20and%20give%20it%20to%