3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20own%20a%20neighborhood%20bar%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20where%20the%20bulk%20of%20what%20we%20sell%20is%20wine.%20There%20weren't%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-worker-left-job-opened-natural-wine-bar-brooklyn-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewine%20bars%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20when%20we%20opened%20nine%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20first%20opened%2C%20we%20had%20to%20establish%20ourselves%2C%20get%20to%20know%20everybody%2C%20be%20good%20stewards%20of%20the%20neighborhood%2C%20and%20gain%20the%20trust%20of%20our%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20COVID%20happened.%20We%20were%20shut%20down%2C%20and%20when%20we%20finally%20reopened%20fully%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20later%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20starting%20over%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20I'm%20starting%20over%20yet%20again.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-problem-small-businesses-exporters-disruptions-delays-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETariffs%20have%20had%20an%20effect%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20the%20industry.%20We%20like%20to%20have%20wines%20from%20a%20variety%20of%20places%20because%20it's%20very%20location-dependent.%20That's%20the%20story%2C%20the%20history%2C%20and%20the%20romance%20of%20it.%20When%20you%20have%20less%20access%20to%20those%20things%20because%20they're%20more%20expensive%2C%20it%20limits%20our%20ability%20to%20have%20a%20variety%20of%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20have%20tariffs%20affected%20you%20as%20a%20customer%20or%20business%20owner%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amhoff%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emhoff%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20have%20little%20kids%2C%20I%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20work%20on%20the%20business%20and%20not%20be%20behind%20the%20bar%20as%20much.%20That's%20changing%20again%2C%20which%20is%20unfortunate%20for%20me%20and%20for%20my%20family.%20It's%20fine.%20It's%20what%20I%20need%20to%20do.%20It's%20my%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERunning%20a%20business%20feels%20harder%20than%20it's%20been%20in%20the%20past%20%E2%80%94%20in%20a%20different%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227c64899d-c50a-4bf7-8ea6-c58cc842ba1b%5C%22%3EThe%20last%20time%20there%20was%20a%20tariff%20war%20like%20this%20was%20the%20last%20time%20Trump%20was%20president%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20some%20wiggle%20room%2C%20though%3A%20Many%20wines%20of%20at%20least%2014%25%20alcohol%20by%20volume%20were%20not%20tariffed.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20a%20number%20of%20the%20distributors%20we%20work%20with%20%E2%80%94%20almost%20exclusively%20small%20businesses%2C%20and%20the%20winemakers%20they%20work%20with%20are%20oftentimes%20solo%20winemakers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20importers%20said%2C%20%3Cem%3EOK%2C%20well%2C%20we're%20just%20going%20to%20kind%20of%20split%20this%20cost.%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20producer's%20going%20to%20take%20a%20hit%2C%20the%20distributor's%20going%20to%20take%20a%20hit%2C%20and%20then%20we're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20raise%20prices%20a%20little%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20it's%20been%20these%20very%20rapid%20tariffs%2C%20and%20nobody%20really%20knows%20if%20they're%20going%20to%20stay.%20A%20number%20of%20distributors%20had%20wine%20that%20was%20already%20here%20and%20not%20subject%20to%20tariffs.%20The%20new%20stuff%20was%2C%20so%20we%20get%20emails%20saying%2C%20%3Cem%3EWe're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20raise%20our%20prices%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20wines%20that%20we%20used%20to%20be%20able%20to%20buy%20at%20a%20certain%20price%20are%20now%20two%20to%20five%20dollars%20more%20a%20bottle%2C%20or%20up%20to%2030%25%20more.%20And%20that%20may%20put%20them%20in%20a%20different%20price%20range%20for%20us%20in%20terms%20of%20what%20we%20can%20turn%20around%20and%20sell%20them%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20fewer%20affordable%20options%20that%20fit%20within%20the%20niche%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffavorite-wines-to-serve-guests-certified-sommelier-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etypes%20of%20wines%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20we%20like%20to%20buy%3A%20small%20production%2C%20low%20intervention%2C%20and%20good%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20wine%20we%20buy%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20increased%20by%20%241.50%20a%20bottle%2C%20from%20%2423%20to%20%2424.50.%20That%20means%20we%20have%20also%20had%20to%20raise%20the%20price%20we%20sell%20it%20for%20%E2%80%94%20from%20%2481%20to%20%2486%20per%20bottle.%20We're%20not%20just%20rebuying%20the%20wines%20when%20they%20increase%20in%20price%20due%20to%20tariffs.%20We%20find%20less%20expensive%20options%20as%20well%20as%20lower%20our%20margins%20on%20many%20of%20the%20wines%20we%20serve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20wines%20come%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20including%20right%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20US.%20We%20haven't%20necessarily%20been%20buying%20more%20domestically%20because%20that%20was%20already%20more%20expensive%20due%20to%20labor%20and%20land%20costs.%20Also%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20labels%2C%20corks%2C%20and%20glass%20come%20from%20all%20different%20places.%20We're%20not%20just%20talking%20about%20crushed%20grapes%20that%20have%20fermented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295bdff7c-e193-4dde-b6b7-07a67d23cb21%5C%22%3EThe%20only%20thing%20coming%20down%20is%20sales%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20sales%20have%20dropped%2026%25%20since%20March%2C%20which%20is%20quite%20significant.%20I%20don't%20attribute%20100%25%20of%20that%20to%20tariffs%2C%20but%20that's%20having%20an%20effect.%20The%20overall%20economy%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20things%20are%20factors.%20This%20is%20why%20we're%20making%20some%20business%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrices%20everywhere%20are%20higher%2C%20so%20people%20are%20going%20out%20less.%20The%20entertainment%20industry%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20has%20been%20hit%20pretty%20hard.%20They're%20working%20less%20frequently%20or%20not%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20lots%20of%20things%20being%20more%20expensive%2C%20we're%20also%20trying%20to%20lower%20our%20prices%20at%20the%20same%20time%20to%20meet%20our%20consumers%20instead%20of%20just%20going%20up%20and%20up%20and%20up.%20This%20is%20very%20tough%20in%20Southern%20California%20because%20labor%20is%20going%20up%2C%20rent%20is%20going%20up%2C%20insurance%20is%20going%20up%2C%20cost%20of%20goods%20is%20going%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20lower%20our%20prices%2C%20we%20need%20to%20find%20different%20products%20of%20similar%20quality%20because%20what%20we%20used%20to%20buy%20is%20now%20more%20expensive.%20So%20our%20prices%20have%20gone%20up%20as%20the%20tariffs%20have%20gone%20up.%20But%20in%20an%20effort%20not%20to%20just%20have%20everything%20continue%20that%20way%2C%20I%20have%20been%20focused%20on%20trying%20to%20find%20lower%20price%20point%20items%20that%20we%20can%20still%20feel%20good%20about%20serving%2C%20so%20that%20our%20overall%20price%20point%20can%20be%20lower.%20However%2C%20we're%20making%20less%20money.%20So%20in%20that%20case%2C%20we're%20taking%20the%20hit%20on%20that%2C%20not%20marking%20up%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20still%20keeping%20prices%20as%20low%20as%20possible%2C%20including%20always%20having%20a%20%249%20glass%20of%20wine%20and%20%246%20draft%20beer%20at%20happy%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2238275227-3abc-4cf2-b19c-0512916048e9%5C%22%3EWe%20are%20focused%20on%20not%20laying%20anybody%20off%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20changed%20in%20and%20out%20times%20a%20little%20bit%20to%20shorten%20the%20hours%20of%20a%20shift.%20The%20bulk%20of%20our%20team's%20wages%20in%20the%20bar%20come%20from%20gratuities%20and%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20might%20call%20out%20or%20go%20on%20vacation%2C%20we%20just%20aren't%20filling%20those%20shifts%20on%20that%20given%20night.%20We%20might%20just%20run%20a%20little%20lean%2C%20or%20I%20might%20come%20in%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20hours%2C%20or%20my%20manager%20will%20work%20more%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20new%20thing%20that%20we've%20been%20talking%20about%20for%20a%20little%20bit%2C%20and%20looking%20at%20how%20to%20make%20these%20adjustments%20without%20severely%20affecting%20anyone's%20income.%20I%20think%20they're%20all%20on%20board%20and%20understand%20why%20we're%20doing%20it%20and%20that%20we're%20trying%20to%20do%20this%20in%20a%20way%20that%20keeps%20their%20best%20interests%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20just%20trying%20to%20stay%20ahead%20of%20it.%20We%20don't%20want%20to%20get%20caught%20in%20a%20place%20where%20we%20are%20bleeding%20money%20and%20then%20don't%20have%20money%20for%20payroll%20or%20to%20pay%20our%20vendors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225c29946b-0fcc-4d96-9cd2-3a96f3bd34fc%5C%22%3EI%20feel%20pretty%20confident%20that%20we%20can%20make%20it%20through%2C%20but%20it%20might%20require%20some%20serious%20changes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20require%20changes%20that%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20make%2C%20which%20would%20be%20having%20to%20lay%20staff%20off%2C%20and%20I%20would%20be%20the%20person%20filling%20in.%20I'm%20aware%20that%20it%20could%20get%20to%20that%20place%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20plan%20for%20it%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20expect%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20we've%20done%20now%20is%20the%20things%20that%20are%20within%20our%20control%2C%20which%20is%20to%20be%20able%20to%20focus%20on%20hospitality%20and%20service%20and%20wine%20education%20for%20our%20team%20so%20that%20we%20can%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20place%20that%20people%20want%20to%20come%20to%20because%20people%20are%20still%20going%20to%20go%20out%20and%20are%20still%20going%20to%20spend%20money%2C%20but%20why%20do%20they%20decide%20to%20come%20to%20our%20place%20tonight%20versus%20somewhere%20else%3F%20That's%20always%20the%20question%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bu