20trade%20fair.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6904541d0be9845f2dc574a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224161%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHyrox's%20founder%20said%20the%20competition%20has%20different%20categories%2C%20so%20normal%20people%20would%20not%20have%20to%20go%20up%20against%20%26quot%3BGreek%20statues.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EHenning%20Kaiser%2Fpicture%20alliance%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHyrox%20has%20categories%20for%20a%20reason%2C%20its%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%2C%20Christian%20Toetzke%2C%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EToetzke%20said%20the%20competition%20was%20designed%20to%20separate%20the%20%26quot%3BGreek%20statues%26quot%3B%20from%20%26quot%3Bnormal%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere%20were%20over%2080%20runs%20of%20Hyrox%20in%202025%2C%20with%20more%20than%20550%2C000%20participants%2C%20per%20its%20website.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHyrox%20was%20designed%20to%20keep%20those%20with%20god-tier%20fitness%20competing%20in%20different%20categories%2C%20and%20not%20alongside%20regular%20people%2C%20its%20cofounder%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BOpening%20Bid%26quot%3B%20podcast%20released%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Hyrox's%20CEO%2C%20Christian%20Toetzke%2C%20spoke%20on%20why%20people%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F70-year-old-fit-after-retiring-tips-getting-active-hyrox-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evastly%20different%20fitness%20levels%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20compete%20in%20the%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-hyrox-race-training-exercises-uk-men-champion-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eviral%20fitness%20competition%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20two%20categories%3A%20the%20open%20and%20the%20pro.%20Those%20competing%20in%20the%20pro%20category%20use%20heavier%20weights%20and%20require%20a%20higher%20level%20of%20fitness%2C%20and%20the%20two%20groups%20are%20kept%20separate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20on%20purpose%2C%26quot%3B%20Toetzke%20told%20host%20Brian%20Sozzi.%20%26quot%3BSo%20the%20guys%20that%20look%20like%20Greek%20statues%20%E2%80%94%20or%20the%20girls%20%E2%80%94%20they%20sign%20up%20for%20the%20pro%20division%2C%20which%20is%20much%20harder%20because%20you%20have%20to%20move%20much%20heavier%20weights%20around.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20you%20feel%20more%20between%20normal%20people%20when%20you%20sign%20up%20for%20the%20open%20category%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20Men%20and%20women%20also%20compete%20separately%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHyrox%2C%20which%20started%20in%202017%20in%20Germany%2C%20requires%20participants%20to%20complete%20eight%20different%20functional%20workout%20stations%2C%20running%20a%20kilometer%20between%20each.%20The%20stations%20include%20workouts%20like%20sled%20pushes%2C%20burpee%20broad%20jumps%2C%20wall%20balls%2C%20and%20sandbag%20lunges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20competition%20has%20risen%20in%20popularity%20since%20its%20inception.%20Hyrox's%20website%20said%20that%20there%20were%20more%20than%2080%20competitions%20planned%20globally%20in%202025%2C%20with%20more%20than%20550%2C000%20participants%20joining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETickets%20for%20the%20competition%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgetting-hyrox-tickets-like-taylor-swift-demand-soaring-fitness-competitions-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20high%20demand%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20some%20fans%20describing%20the%20effort%20to%20secure%20them%20as%20comparable%20to%20securing%20tickets%20for%20Glastonbury%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-taylor-swift-tickets-regret-spending-eras-ticketmaster-stubhub-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETaylor%20Swift's%20concerts%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Toetzke%20said%20in%20the%20podcast%20that%20the%20tickets%20are%20priced%20around%2