E%20using%20Nuro's%20self-driving%20technology%20and%20Lucid's%20Gravity%20SUV%2C%20a%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Enearly%20%2480%2C000%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFerguson%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20Gravity%20will%20help%20capture%20riders%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-quiet-driver-mode-how-to-request-it-features-details-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUber%20Black%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20ride-hailing%20platform's%20premium%20service%2C%20as%20well%20as%20UberXL%20and%20UberX.%20That%20doesn't%20mean%20the%20Nuro%20Driver%20won't%20be%20in%20other%20vehicle%20platforms%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20Ferguson%20at%20TechCrunch%20Disrupt%20in%20San%20Francisco%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20lessons%20he's%20learned%20at%20Google's%20self-driving%20car%20project%2C%20why%20he%20believes%20he%20can%20compete%20with%20what%20is%20now%20Waymo%2C%20and%20what%20it%20will%20take%20to%20scale%20robotaxis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20interview%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20take%20Waymos%20often%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20do.%20I%20love%20it.%20JZ%2C%20my%20cofounder%2C%20and%20I%20were%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-bonus-equity-plan-self-driving-car-waymo-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20self-driving%20car%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20we%20left%20just%20before%20it%20was%20renamed%20Waymo.%20I've%20basically%20spent%20my%20whole%20career%20on%20self-driving%2C%20so%20being%20in%20a%20Waymo%20is%20still%20a%20real%20treat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20it%20like%20to%20meet%20your%20alma%20mater%20on%20the%20public%20stage%20in%20San%20Francisco%20nine%20years%20after%20founding%20Nuro%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20great.%20We%20still%20have%20a%20great%20relationship%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20key%20folks.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-new-ceos-tekedra-mawakana-dmitri-dolgov-john-krafcik-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDmitri%20(Waymo's%20Co-CEO)%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20still%20a%20friend%2C%20an%20amazing%20guy.%20I%20think%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20love%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20go%20back%20far%20enough%2C%20the%20original%20genesis%20of%20the%20self-driving%20industry%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20US%2C%20is%20a%20very%20small%20group%20of%20people%20from%20a%20few%20universities.%20It's%20a%20pretty%20tight-knit%20community%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20many%20of%20us%20are%20now%20at%20different%20companies.%20Some%20of%20it%20may%20be%20competitive%2C%20some%20may%20be%20collaborative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20there%20lessons%20you've%20learned%20from%20Google%20that%20you've%20applied%20to%20founding%20Nuro%20and%20now%20deploying%20robotaxis%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20is%20everything.%20For%20JZ%20and%20I%2C%20when%20we%20started%20Nuro%2C%20it%20was%20critical%20to%20us%20that%20we%20put%20together%20a%20team%20of%20the%20absolute%20best%20talent.%20A-players%20attract%20A-players.%20Looking%20back%20nine%20years%20later%2C%20that%20is%20where%20all%20of%20the%20success%20we%20may%20have%20had%20can%20be%20attributed%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20make%20sure%20that%20you're%20working%20on%20something%20that%20matters%20and%20that%20you%20have%20strategic%20clarity.%20It's%20not%20enough%20to%20just%20build%20great%20tech.%20You%20have%20to%20have%20figured%20out%20the%20path%20to%20get%20that%20tech%20to%20actually%20do%20something%20interesting%20and%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20this%20exclusive%20partnership%20with%20Uber%3A%20Does%20it%20give%20Uber%20the%20opportunity%20to%20tell%20other%20companies%20like%20Waymo%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20we%20know%20you%20guys%20are%20doing%20your%20own%20thing%2C%20well%2C%20we%20have%20our%20own%20service%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20an%20opportunity%20for%20Uber%20to%20play%20a%20really%20key%20role%20in%20deciding%20what%20the%20product%20will%20be%3A%20the%20in-car%20experience%2C%20the%20hailing%20experience%2C%20pickup%2C%20and%20drop-off.%20So%20it%20was%20an%20opportunity%20for%20Uber%20to%20be%20much%20more%20involved%20in%20the%20design%20of%20the%20product%20piece.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20consumer%20proposition%3F%20Many%20people%20simply%20want%20the%20cheapest%20and%20quickest%20ride.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber's%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-focusing-on-suburbs-grow-ride-hailing-business-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elargest%20ride-hailing%20network%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20world%2C%20so%20there's%20an%20incredible%20economy%20of%20scale%20there.%20There's%20no%20reason%2C%20long-term%2C%20that%20Uber%20won't%20have%20a%20product%20that%20both%20blows%20people%20away%20in%20terms%20of%20quality%20user%20experience%20and%20is%20the%20one%20leading%20in%20terms%20of%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227285%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lucid%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69040ab5c007ca8c2737fadc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELucid's%20Gravity%20SUV%20will%20be%20installed%20with%20Nuro's%20self-driving%20technology%20for%20Uber's%20robotaxi%20fleet.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Nuro%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGravity%20is%20a%20premium%20vehicle.%20It's%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20capture%20a%20lot%20of%20Uber's%20current%20wide%20market%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20premium%20side%2C%20Uber%20Black.%20It%20will%20also%20be%20able%20to%20capture%20UberXL%20and%20UberX.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20be%20other%20(vehicle)%20platforms%20with%20Lucid%20that%20will%20be%20a%20lower%20price%20point%20that%20perhaps%20will%20scale%20for%20UberX%2C%20but%20even%20the%20Gravity%20itself%20is%20going%20to%20provide%20a%20compelling%20price%20proposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20reason%20for%20that%20is%20that%20the%20technology%20that%20Nuro%20is%20bringing%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20the%20sensing%20and%20compute%20%E2%80%94%20is%20dramatically%20less%20expensive%20than%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EL4%20players%3C%2Fa%3E%20today.%20So%20even%20if%20the%20vehicle%20is%20not%20incredibly%20low-cost%2C%20it's%20still%20very%20cost-effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20the%20sensor%20stack%20much%20lighter%20than%20Waymo's%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-robotaxi-lidar-sensor-versus-cameras-vision-only-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20camera%2C%20lidar%2C%20radar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20it's%20all%20of%20the%20usual%20suspects.%20However%2C%20it%20utilizes%20off-the-shelf%2C%20automotive-grade%20sensors%2C%20so%20we%20don't%20have%20to%20manufacture%20any%20custom%20sensors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELucid%20designed%20an%20incredibly%20beautiful%20vehicle%2C%20and%20we%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20that%2C%20when%20we%20installed%20the%20sensor%20stack%2C%20it%20didn't%20detract%20from%20that%20and%20suddenly%20make%20it%20look%20like%20a%20Frankenstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20spinning%20lidar%3B%20all%20solid%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsumers%20may%20see%20edge-case%20stories%20like%20a%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmalfunctioning-waymo-trapped-passenger-inside-drove-in-circles-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Erobotaxi%20driving%20in%20circles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20and%20think%20that%20the%20technology%20isn't%20quite%20there.%20How%20do%20you%20close%20that%20gap%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it%20will%20close%20over%20time.%20We're%20already%20at%20the%20point%20where%20the%20technology%20has%20proven%20that%20it%20is%20not%20only%20capable%20of%20being%20a%20product%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20preferred%20product%20over%20the%20alternative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20yes%2C%20there%20will%20still%20be%20some%20edges%20that%20need%20smoothing%2C%20and%20there%20are%20still%20some%20technical%20improvements%20that%20we'll%20all%20make%20over%20time%2C%20but%20it's%20already%20at%20a%20point%20where%20people%20prefer%20the%20alternative%2C%20which%20is%20an%20incredible%20place%20for%20it%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20those%20key%20technical%20challenges%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20general%20challenges%20include%20expanding%20to%20all%20weather%2C%20particularly%20snow.%20That's%20something%20most%20of%20us%20in%20this%20space%20have%20held%20off%20on%20because%20there's%20a%20huge%20opportunity%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20impact%20that%20we%20can%20have%20before%20needing%20to%20tackle%20snow.%20However%2C%20we%20have%20confidence%20that%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20lidar%20vs.%20camera%20debate%3A%20How%20do%20you%20see%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20strongly%20believe%20that%20lidar%20is%20a%20highly%20valuable%20sensor%20for%20fully%20autonomous%20driving.%20But%20it's%20not%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-vs-waymo-what-ceos-eautonomous-automotive-leaders-say-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elidar%20versus%20camera%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20because%20everyone%20is%20going%20to%20use%20cameras.%20The%20question%20is%3A%20Should%20we%20put%20lidars%20on%20that%20car%20or%20not%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20physics%20perspective%2C%20it's%20complementary%20information%20to%20what%20you%20get%20from%20a%20camera.%20If%20you%20have%20an%20AI%20system%20with%20cameras%2C%20radars%2C%20and%20then%20lidar%20%E2%80%94%20because%20there%20is%20some%20non-redundant%20information%20that's%20coming%20off%20that%20lidar%20%E2%80%94%20that%20AI%20system%20should%20theoretically%20be%20able%20to%20do%20a%20better%20job.%20So%2C%20from%20a%20theoretical%20perspective%2C%20the%20ceiling%20is%20higher%20if%20you%20have%20lidar.%20The%20question%20is%20how%20much%20higher%3F%20How%20much%20value%20are%20you%20actually%20getting%20from%20the%20lidar%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20actual%20hardware%20cost%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20no-brainer.%20When%20we%20started%20at%20Google%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20single%20lidar%20was%20like%20%2475%2C000.%20Today%2C%20it's%20like%20500%20bucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20if%20there%20is%20any%20incremental%20benefit%20you're%20getting%20from%20having%20a%20lidar%2C%20then%20it%20becomes%20a%20pretty%20easy%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20you're%20not%20saying%20cameras-only%20won't%20work%2C%20right%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20the%20argument%20is%20that%2C%20as%20humans%2C%20we%20have%20two%20cameras.%20So%2C%20theoretically%2C%20if%20humans%20can%20drive%2C%20then%20cameras%20on%20your%20system%20should%20be%20able%20to%20do%20it.%20I%20think%20there%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20challenges%20with%20that%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cameras%20that%20we%20have%20today%20are%20not%20nearly%20as%20good%20as%20our%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20point%20is%2C%20even%20if%20you%20can%20have%20a%20system%20that%20can%20drive%20as%20well%20as%20a%20human%20with%20just%20today's%20cameras%20%E2%80%94%20if%20it's%20%24500%20extra%20to%20add%20a%20lidar%20and%20it's%20going%20to%20increase%20the%20safety%20of%20that%20system%20significantly%2C%20why%20would%20you%20not%20do%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20great%20bottleneck%20then%20for%20robotaxis%3F%20Is%20it%20the%20technology%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20or%20even%20human%20adoption%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it's%20really%20about%20scaling%20fleets%2C%20that%20is%2C%20having%20a%20vehicle%20that%20is%20low-cost%20enough%20and%20available