nessinsider.com%2Ftech%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20drive%20growth.%20This%20compares%20with%20just%20one%20in%20five%20deploying%20it%20primarily%20to%20cut%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20only%20about%20one%20in%2010%20firms%20has%20reduced%20head%20count%20so%20far%20due%20to%20AI%2C%20though%20nearly%20a%20third%20of%20bankers%20covering%20technology%2C%20media%2C%20and%20telecom%20clients%20report%20early%20signs%20of%20job%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20bankers%20expect%20AI%20to%20start%20trimming%20payrolls%20soon.%20They%20forecast%20a%204%25%20reduction%20in%20head%20count%20over%20the%20next%20year%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20deeper%2011%25%20cut%20within%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20relatively%20fast%20increase%20in%20expected%20adoption%20and%20head%20count%20reductions%20over%20the%20next%20three%20years%20highlights%20that%20AI%20impacts%20on%20the%20US%20labor%20market%20could%20arrive%20sooner%20than%20expected%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Goldman's%20analysts%2C%20led%20by%20chief%20economist%20Jan%20Hatzius%2C%20in%20a%20Thursday%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222fb6369a-842b-485a-9873-92332fd73c67%5C%22%3ECustomer%20support%20is%20most%20at%20risk%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2055%25%20of%20Goldman's%20bankers%20expect%20clients%20to%20rely%20on%20hiring%20freezes%20or%20natural%20attrition%20as%20AI%20reshapes%20roles%2C%20while%2026%25%20anticipate%20layoffs%20or%20broader%20restructuring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman's%20bankers%20also%20see%20the%20most%20significant%20potential%20for%20AI-driven%20reductions%20in%20head%20count%20in%20customer%20support%2C%20where%2080%25%20of%20respondents%20expect%20cuts%20as%20automation%20takes%20hold.%20Other%20positions%20at%20risk%20include%20those%20in%20administrative%20support%2C%20operations%20at%2049%25%2C%20and%20IT%20and%20engineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman's%20report%20lands%20amid%20a%20wave%20of%20recent%20layoffs%20