onal%20seeds%20to%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20enhanced%20their%20income%20as%20well.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FgreenDay-1-1725603304-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364813%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20By%20encouraging%20the%20shift%20from%20traditional%20seeds%20to%20biofortified%20seeds%2C%20farmers%20enhanced%20their%20income%20as%20well.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20further%2C%20Prateek%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20we%20found%20that%20the%20baseline%20levels%20of%20zinc%20in%20the%20traditional%20variety%20of%20wheat%20is%20around%2028%20parts%20per%20million%20whereas%2C%20it%20is%2045%20parts%20per%20million%20in%20the%20newer%20bio%20fortified%20seeds.%20We%20also%20add%20a%20zinc%20soil%20bacteria%20to%20the%20soil%20which%20helps%20mobilise%20the%20naturally%20available%20zinc%20and%20bring%20it%20to%20the%20roots.%20This%20increases%20zinc%20base%20levels%20to%2050-55%20parts%20per%20million%20%E2%80%93%20an%20increment%20of%20about%2080%20percent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20every%20seed%20will%20have%20its%20own%20benefits%20and%20drawbacks.%20These%20seeds%20give%20almost%2080%20percent%20more%20nutritional%20value%20but%20farmers%20may%20have%20to%20take%20a%20dip%20of%204%20to%205%20percent%20in%20yield.%20But%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F